{"sn10.2:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 10.2 ","sn10.2:0.2":"1. Indakavagga ","sn10.2:0.3":"Sakkanamasutta ","sn10.2:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava rajagahe viharati gijjhakute pabbate. ","sn10.2:1.2":"Atha kho sakkanamako yakkho yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn10.2:2.1":"“Sabbaganthappahinassa, ","sn10.2:2.2":"vippamuttassa te sato; ","sn10.2:2.3":"Samanassa na tam sadhu, ","sn10.2:2.4":"yadannamanusasasi”ti. ","sn10.2:3.1":"“Yena kenaci vannena, ","sn10.2:3.2":"samvaso sakka jayati; ","sn10.2:3.3":"Na tam arahati sappanno, ","sn10.2:3.4":"manasa anukampitum. ","sn10.2:4.1":"Manasa ce pasannena, ","sn10.2:4.2":"yadannamanusasati; ","sn10.2:4.3":"Na tena hoti samyutto, ","sn10.2:4.4":"yanukampa anuddaya”ti. "}